20Criticism%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERoyal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20(RCB)%20stalwart%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Indian%20cricket%20legend%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sunil%20Gavaskar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F40594-sunil-manohar-gavaskar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESunil%20Gavaskar%3C%2Fa%3E%20engaged%20in%20an%20unexpected%20battle%20of%20words%20over%20the%20batter's%20'strike-rate'%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202024.%20Gavaskar%20has%20been%20regularly%20criticising%20Kohli%20over%20his%20inability%20to%20get%20into%20ulra-attacking%20mode%20and%20rescue%20RCB's%20campaign.%20However%2C%20Virat%20decided%20to%20hit%20back%20at%20all%20those%20criticising%20him%20over%20his%20strike-rate%2C%20but%20little%20did%20he%20expect%20that%20the%20cricketer-turned-commentator%20Gavaskar%20would%20be%20sharp%20with%20his%20reply%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20there%20continues%20to%20remain%20a%20back-and-forth%20between%20Kohli%20and%20Gavaskar%2C%20former%20Australia%20opener%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Matthew%20Hayden%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F219-matthew-hayden-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMatthew%20Hayden%3C%2Fa%3E%20jumped%20into%20the%20debate%2C%20saying%20he%20expects%20nothing%20but%20fireworks%20from%20Virat%20at%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20strike%20rate%20is%20trending%20in%20the%20right%20direction%2C%20it's%20trending%20up.%20Look%20at%20the%20IPL%20over%20the%20last%20four%20years%2C%20it's%20gone%20from%20mid%20and%20around%20that%20120%20then%20it%20goes%20130%20and%20then%20140%20and%20150.%20So%20150%20for%20me%20is%20kind%20of%20that%20sweet%20spot%20that%20starts%20in%20and%20everyone%20having%20conversation%20well%20where%20you%20bat%3F%20Is%20it%20t