ot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EHoping%20that%20this%20%E2%80%9Cpronoun%20illness%E2%80%9D%20doesn't%20reach%20India.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMany%20%E2%80%9Cbig%20city%20schools%E2%80%9D%20in%20India%20are%20now%20teaching%20it%20to%20kids.%20Also%20see%20many%20CVs%20with%20pronouns%20these%20days.%20Need%20to%20know%20where%20to%20draw%20the%20line%20in%20following%20the%20west%20blindly!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fq4CwiV6dkE%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fq4CwiV6dkE%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Bhavish%20Aggarwal%20(%40bhash)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbhash%2Fstatus%2F1787191204104532074%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%205%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ECircling%20the%20%26quot%3Bthey%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Btheirs%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20AI%20bot's%20reply%2C%20Mr%20Aggarwal%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BHoping%20that%20this%20'pronoun%20illness'%20doesn't%20reach%20India.%20Many%20'big%20city%20schools'%20in%20India%20are%20now%20teaching%20it%20to%20kids.%20Also%20see%20many%20CVs%20with%20pronouns%20these%20days.%20Need%20to%20know%20where%20to%20draw%20the%20line%20in%20following%20the%20west%20blindly!%20Screenshot%20is%20from%20LinkedIns%20AI%20bot.%20This%20'pronouns%20illness'%20is%20being%20perpetuated%20in%20India%20by%20MNCs%20without%20us%20Indians%20even%20realising%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20follow-up%20post%2C%20Mr%20Aggarwal%20said%20that%20most%20Indians%20have%20no%20clue%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Bpolitics%20of%20pronoun%20illness%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20that%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bbetter%20to%20send%20this%20illness%20back.%20He%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BPeople%20do%20it%20because%20it's%20become%20expected%20in%20our%20corporate%20culture%2C%20especially%20MNCs.%20Better%20to%20send%20this%20illness%20back%20where%20it%20came%20from.%20Our%20culture%20has%20always%20had%20respect%20for%20all.%20No%20need%20for%20new%20pronouns.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20being%20shared%2C%20the%20post%20has%20amassed%20over%20a%20million%20views%20and%20has%20drawn%20mixed%20reactions%20online.%20Many%20users%20also%20expressed%20their%20disappointment%20after%20reading%20Mr%20Aggarwal's%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20disagree%20with%20you%20here.%20This%20doesn't%20hurt%20anyone%20and%20do%20you%20really%20think%20having%20pronouns%20on%20CVs%20would%20impact%20your%20decision%20to%20hire%20an%20individual%3F%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20second%20X%20person%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BRespecting%20pronouns%20is%20a%20basic%20act%20of%20decency%2C%20not%20an%20illness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUsing%20someone's%20correct%20pronouns%20is%20the%20bare%20minimum%2C%20to%20respect%20LGBTQ%2B%20folks.%20You're%20tweeting%20this%20just%20a%20month%20before%20Pride%20Month%20is%20celebrated%20and%20I'd%20suggest%20you%20take%20this%20time%20to%20follow%20thought%20Queer%20leaders%20in%20India%20to%20understand%20their%20journey%2C%20struggles%20and%20needs%2C%26quot%3B%20remarked%20a%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20social%20media%20user%20commented%2C%20%26quot%3BCalling%20it%20as%20illness%20is%20way%20beneath%20you%20as%20an%20industry%20leader%20bhavish%2C%20yes%20it%20was%20wrong%20on%20LinkedIn%20part%20use%20non%20binary%20pronouns%20as%20default%20when%20you%20identify%20with%20he%2Fhim%2C%20although%20mocking%20the%20pronouns%20and%20how%20people%20chose%20to%20identify%20themselves%20is%20disgusting%2C%20DELETE%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20am%20I%20not%20surprised%3F%20Just%20disappointed%20in%20you.%20Such%20potential.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20person%20commented%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20violated%20me%20with%20your%20homophobia!%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BIf%20you%20didn't%20live%20under%20the%20rock%2C%20you'd%20know%20that%20our%20generation%20of%20Indians%20happily%20evolved%20long%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20commet%20read%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20reached...%20backed%20by%20MNCs%20and%20Social%20Media!%20Infact%20in%20some%20companies%20not%20having%20a%20pronoun%20in%20your%20signature%20or%20internal%20profile%20can%20get%20you%20sidelined%20for%20promotions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20person%20also%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BThank%20god.%20There%20is%20hope.%20A%20CEO%20and%20influencer%20speaking%20against%20this%20illness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTotally%20agree.%20We%20cannot%20import%20it%20when%20we%20have%20real%20issues%20on%20the%20ground.%20But%20this%20is%20up%20to%20the%20MNCs%20and%20government%20of%20India.%20Employees%20will%20be%20forced%20to%20follow%20it%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20stated%20a%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714991640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-04%2F4ghk9bpg_bhavish-aggarwal_625x300_12_April_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fola-ceo-bhavish-aggarwal-sparks-debate-on-gender-pronouns-calls-it-illness-5600728%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mr%20Aggarwal%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHoping%20that%20this%20'pronoun%20illness'%20doesn't%20reach%20India.%20Many%20'big%20city%20schools'%20in%20India%20are%20now%20teaching%20it%20to%20kids.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fola-ceo-bhavish-aggarwal-sparks-debate-on-gender-pronouns-calls-it-illness-5600728%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fola-ceo-bhavish-aggarwal-sparks-debate-on-gender-pronouns-calls-it-illness-5600728%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fola-ceo-bhavish-aggarwal-sparks-debate-on-gender-pronouns-calls-it-illness-5600728%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Ram%20droh'%3A%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20on%20