om%20Dalit%2C%20backward%20and%20tribal%20communities%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20poll%20rally%20at%20Ratlam%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said%20this%20election%20is%20being%20fought%20to%20save%20the%20Constitution.%20%26quot%3BBJP%20and%20RSS%20want%20to%20finish%20this%2C%20change%20this.%20And%20the%20Congress%20and%20INDIA%20bloc%20are%20trying%20to%20save%20this.%20This%20Constitution%20has%20given%20you%20rights%20on%20jal%20(water)%2C%20jangal%20(forest)%2C%20zameen%20(land).%20Narendra%20Modi%20wants%20to%20remove%20them%2C%20he%20wants%20full%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20holding%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20he%20said%2C%20had%20declared%20that%20they%20would%20change%20the%20Constitution%20if%20they%20win.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20they%20gave%20the%20'400%20seats'%20slogan.%20But%20forget%20400%2C%20they%20are%20not%20getting%20150%20seats.%20They%20say%20they%20will%20remove%20reservation.%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20you%20from%20this%20stage%2C%20we%20will%20increase%20reservation%20beyond%20the%2050%20per%20cent%20cap.%20We%20will%20give%20as%20much%20reservation%20as%20needed%20for%20the%20poor%2C%20the%20backwards%2C%20Dalits%20and%20adivasis%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi's%20remarks%20come%20amid%20a%20high-pitched%20campaign%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20and%20heated%20exchanges%20between%20the%20NDA%20and%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20on%20reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20Congress%20plans%20to%20tinker%20with%20the%20reservation%20for%20backward%20classes%20to%20benefit%20Muslims.%20The%20Congress%20has%20denied%20the%20allegations.%20At%20a%20rally%20in%20Gujarat%20Banaskantha%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20challenge%20the%20'shehzada'%20of%20the%20Congress%20as%20well%20as%20his%20party%20and%20its%20supporters%20to%20announce%20they%20will%20never%20misuse%20reservation%20in%20the%20name%20of%20religion%2C%20nor%20will%20they%20play%20with%20the%20Constitution%20or%20grant%20reservation%20in%20the%20name%20of%20religion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Ratlam%20rally%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said%20the%20media%20does%20not%20show%20news%20related%20to%20atrocities%20on%20Adivasis.%20%26quot%3BYour%20children%20are%20raped%2C%20your%20land%20is%20snatched%2C%20but%20media%20does%20not%20report.%20There%20is%20a%20reason.%20There%20are%20no%20Adivasis%20in%20these%20media%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20said%2090%20bureaucrats%20run%20the%20country's%20government.%20%26quot%3BThey%20distribute%20the%20budgets.%20Only%201%20out%20of%20the%2090%20is%20an%20Adivasis%2C%20three%20are%20from%20backward%20classes%2C%20three%20from%20the%20Dalit%20community.%20Your%20people%20are%20neither%20in%20the%20media%20nor%20the%20corporate%20world.%20We%20want%20to%20change%20this.%20This%20is%20why%20we%20have%20decided%20to%20carry%20out%20a%20caste%20Census%20and%20an%20economic%20survey%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20also%20assured%20farmers%20relief%20in%20the%20form%20of%20assured%20MSP%20and%20loan%20waivers.%C2%A0%26quot%3BThese%20are%20our%20guarantees.%20They%20will%20change%20your%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERatlam%20votes%20on%20May%2013%20in%20the%20fourth%20phase%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20The%20Congress%20has%20fielded%20former%20MP%20and%20former%20Union%20Minister%20Kantilal%20Bhuria.%20Anita%20Nagar%20Singh%20Chauhan%20is%20the%20BJP's%20pick%20from%20the%20seat%20they%20won%20in%20the%202019%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714990140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fifu02pt_rahul-gandhi-ratlam_625x300_06_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%