ory%20margin%20of%2021%25%20was%20much%20higher%20than%20that%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc's%2011%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20won%2038%20seats%20with%20a%2050-60%25%20vote%20share%20in%20the%20last%20election%2C%2020%20seats%20with%20a%2060-70%25%20vote%20share%2C%20and%20two%20seats%20with%20an%20over%2070%25%20votes.%20The%20Congress%20thus%20needs%20a%20big%20swing%20in%20its%20favour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-polls-2024-blow-to-congress-as-200-members-join-bjp-in-gujarat-5593914%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Lok%20Sabha%20Polls%202024%3A%20Blow%20To%20Congress%20As%20200%20Members%20Join%20BJP%20In%20Gujarat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETurnout%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20key%20factor%20as%20the%20first%20two%20phases%20saw%20a%20drop%20in%20polling%20by%20around%203%20percentage%20points.%20In%202019%2C%20of%20the%2062%20seats%20in%20which%20the%20turnout%20had%20declined%2C%20the%20winner%20changed%20for%2014%20seats.%20In%20contrast%2C%20of%20the%2031%20seats%20that%20saw%20higher%20voting%2C%20the%20incumbent%20lost%20in%20nine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20West%20Bengal%20Battleground%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20West%20Bengal%2C%20the%20electoral%20contest%20moves%20to%20the%20Malda%20region%2C%20which%20has%20a%20high%20minority%20population%20(Malda%2C%20Murshidabad%2C%20Jangipur).%20This%20is%20a%20traditional%20Congress%20stronghold%2C%20though%20the%20party%20won%20only%20the%20Malda%20Dakshin%20seat%20in%202019.%20Due%20to%20a%20split%20of%20votes%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Trinamool%2C%20the%20BJP%20ended%20up%20getting%20the%20Malda%20Uttar%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20the%20Congress-Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20(CPI-M)%20alliance%20is%20vying%20for%20the%20minority%20vote%20here.%20In%20the%20last%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20got%2063%25%20of%20the%20Muslim%20vote%20and%20the%20Congress-CPI(M)%20alliance%20got%2016%25.%20The%20impact%20of%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20(CAA)%20could%20be%20visible%20here.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Gujarat%20Fortress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGujarat%20is%20the%20BJP's%20fortress%2C%20and%20the%20'Gujarati%20%3Cem%3Easmita%3C%2Fem%3E'%20plays%20a%20key%20role%20here%20as%20both%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20hail%20from%20the%20state.%20The%20real%20question%20is%20whether%20the%20party%20can%20score%20a%20hat-trick%20of%2026-0%20this%20year%2C%20riding%20on%20its%20strong%20performance%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls%20in%202022.%20On%2018%20seats%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20with%20a%20lead%20of%20over%202.5%20lakh%20votes%3B%20its%20victory%20in%20all%20seats%20was%20with%20an%20over%2050%25%20vote%20share.%20While%20the%20all-India%20lead%20of%20the%20BJP%20over%20the%20Congress%20is%2019%25%20in%20terms%20of%20vote%20share%2C%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20that%20number%20is%20a%20whopping%2030%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-polls-in-gujarat-bjps-richest-candidate-poonamben-maadam-has-assets-worth-rs-147-ccrore-5549515%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0In%20Gujarat%2C%20BJP's%20Richest%20Candidate%20Has%20Assets%20Worth%20Rs%20147%20Crore%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20is%20some%20unease%20within%20the%20Kshatriya%2FRajput%20community%20over%20Union%20Minister%20Parshottam%20Rupala's%20statements%2C%20who%20is%20contesting%20from%20Rajkot.%20As%20many%20as%2065%25%20Rajputs%20voted%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%202019.%20The%20discontent%20has%20given%20an%20opportunity%20to%20the%20Congress%20to%20revive%20its%20KHAM%20(Kshtriya-Harijan-Adivasi-Muslim)%20vote%20bank.%20The%20Congress%20has%20formed%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%2C%20which%20had%20dented%20the%20former's%20vote%20share%20in%20the%202022%20Assembly%20elections.%20As%20per%20ground%20reports%2C%20Banaskantha%2C%20Rajkot%20and%20Valsad%20are%20witnessing%20close%20contests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EVarious%20Factors%20At%20Play%20In%20UP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20battle%20will%20involve%20a%20few%20seats%20in%20the%20Western%20part%20of%20the%20state%20and%20the%20Yadav%20belt.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%2C%20with%20a%20stronger%20Mahagathbandhan%20alliance%20with%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%2C%20won%20two%20of%20the%2010%20seats%20that%20are%20going%20to%20polls%20this%20time.%20The%20Congress%20cannot%20be%20expected%20to%20replace%20the%20BSP%20in%20the%20alliance.%20Over%2070%25%20of%20Muslims%2C%20Yadavs%20and%20Jatavs%20had%20backed%20the%20Mahagathbandan%20in%202019.%20This%20time%20around%2C%20the%20Jatav%20support%20could%20see%20a%20dent%2C%20which%20could%20go%20back%20to%20the%20BSP%20as%20it%20contests%20separately.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Etah%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20won%20more%20times%20than%20the%20SP.%20Kalyan%20Singh%20won%20once%20from%20here%20in%202009%2C%20though%20that%20was%20in%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20SP.%20Mainpuri%20is%20an%20SP%20stronghold%20too.%20Both%20these%20seats%20have%20strong%20Scheduled%20Caste%20and%20Yadav%20populations.%20In%20the%20previous%20election%2C%20the%20average%20vote%20share%20of%20the%20BJP%20here%20was%2054%25%2C%20while%20the%20Mahagathbandhan's%20was%2037%25.%20The%20Jat%20factor%20will%20also%20come%20into%20play%20in%20a%20few%20seats%20given%20the%20BJP's%20tie-up%20with%20Jayant%20Chaudhary's%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20(RLD).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EKarnataka%20And%20The%20Shadow%20Of%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20Scandal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%2014%20seats%20of%20Northern%20and%20Central%20Karnataka%20go%20to%20polls%2C%20of%20which%20the%20BJP%20had%20swept%20all%20in%202019.%20While%20Bombay%20Karnataka%20has%20a%20big%20Lingayat%20population%2C%20Hyderabad%20Karnataka%2C%20from%20where%20Congress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20comes%20(Gulbarga)%2C%20has%20a%20considerable%20SC-ST%20population.%20With%20the%20return%20of%20Jagadish%20Shettar%20and%20the%20appointment%20of%20B.S.%20Yediyurappa's%20son%20as%20the%20state%20unit's%20president%2C%20the%20BJP%20hopes%20to%20get%20back%20a%20section%20of%20Lingayat%20votes%20that%20had%20moved%20to%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%202023%20assembly%20election.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20sexual%20harassment%20case%20looms%20large%20over%20the%20electoral%20contest%20here%20and%20has%20been%20a%20subject%20of%20intense%20discussion%20even%20though%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20is%20not%20contesting%20any%20seat%20in%20this%20phase.%20The%20party%20got%20a%20crucial%207%25%20votes%20here%20in%202019.%20The%20Congress%20hopes%20that%20the%20controversy%20will%20consolidate%20its%20support%20among%20women%2C%20which%20is%20already%20strong%20due%20to%20the%20state%20government's%20implementation%20of%20various%20guarantees.%20Karnataka%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20states%20where%20the%20Congress%20hopes%20to%20make%20a%20significant%20dent%20in%20the%20BJP's%20tally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Leadership%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%3B%20Family%20Feuds%20In%20Maharashtra%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20new%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20with%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20tied%20to%20Vidisha%2C%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20BJP%20unit%20hopes%20to%20maintain%20its%20winning%20streak%20under%20a%20new%20leadership.%20The%20Congress%2C%20which%20has%20put%20up%20old%20warhorses%20like%20Digvijay%20Singh%20and%20Kantilal%20Bhuria%2C%20is%20also%20aiming%20to%20pull%20a%20few%20seats%2C%20banking%20on%20local%20anti-incumbency%20against%20MPs.%20The%20BJP%20had%20won%20a%20record%20term%20with%20166%20seats%20in%20the%20Madhya%20Prades