ps%20Class%2010%2C%2012%20Merit%20Lists%20To%20Avoid%20Unhealthy%20Competition%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Council%20for%20the%20Indian%20School%20Certificate%20Examinations%20(CISCE)%20has%20announced%20the%20discontinuation%20of%20releasing%20merit%20lists%20for%20the%20Class%2010%20and%20Class%2012%20exams%20in%20order%20to%20prevent%20unhealthy%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20discontinued%20the%20practice%20of%20releasing%20merit%20lists%20for%20board%20exams%20from%20this%20year.%20The%20move%20is%20aimed%20at%20avoiding%20unhealthy%20competition%20among%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20news%20agency%20PTI%20quoted%20CISCE%20chief%20executive%20and%20secretary%20Joseph%20Emmanuel%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20Central%20Board%20of%20Secondary%20Education%20(CBSE)%20discontinued%20the%20practice%20of%20releasing%20merit%20lists%20for%20the%20board%20exams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Council%20for%20the%20Indian%20School%20Certificate%20Examinations%20(CISCE)%20declared%20the%20results%20for%20the%20Indian%20Certificate%20of%20Secondary%20Education%20(ICSE%20Class%2010)%20and%20Indian%20School%20Certificate%20(ISC%20Class%2012)%20for%202024%20on%20Monday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pass%20rates%20for%20Class%2010%20and%20Class%2012%20stand%20at%2099.47%25%20and%2098.19%25%2C%20respectively.%20Girls%20have%20outperformed%20boys%20in%20both%20ICSE%20(Class%2010)%20and%20ISC%20(Class%2012)%20with%20pass%20rates%20of%2099.65%25%20and%2098.92%25%2C%20respectively.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20approximately%203.43%20lakh%20students%20took%20the%20CISCE%20examinations%20for%20classes%2010%20and%2012.%20In%20the%20Class%2010%20final%20exam%2C%201%2C30%2C506%20boys%20and%201%2C13%2C111%20girls%20appeared%2C%20with%201%2C29%2C612%20boys%20and%201%2C12%2C716%20girls%20passing.%20In%20the%20Class%2012%20exam%2C%2047%2C136%20girls%20and%2052%2C765%20boys%20appeared%2C%20with%2046%2C626%20girls%20and%2051%2C462%20boys%20passing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20western%20region%20of%20the%20country%20achieved%20the%20highest%20pass%20rate%20for%20Class%2010%20at%2099.91%25%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20Southern%20region%20with%20a%20pass%20rate%20of%2099.88%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutside%20India%2C%20schools%20in%20Indonesia%2C%20Singapore%2C%20and%20Dubai%20(UAE)%20demonstrated%20the%20best%20performance%20with%20a%20100%25%20pass%20rate%20for%20Class%2010%2C%20while%20schools%20in%20Singapore%20and%20Dubai%20(UAE)%20achieved%20a%20100%25%20pass%20rate%20for%20Class%2012.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICSE%20examinations%20covered%2060%20written%20subjects%2C%20including%2020%20Indian%20languages%2C%2013%20foreign%20languages%2C%20and%20one%20classical%20language%2C%20held%20from%20February%2021%20to%20March%2028%20across%2018%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ISC%20examinations%20were%20held%20for%2047%20written%20subjects%2C%20comprising%2012%20Indian%20languages%2C%20four%20foreign%20languages%2C%20and%20two%20classical%20languages%2C%20conducted%20from%20February%2012%20to%20April%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714987020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2F8bkdqni_cbse-class-12-pass-outs_625x300_12_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fafter-cbse-cisce-scraps-class-10-12-merit-lists-to-avoid-unhealthy-competition-5600074%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22ICSE%2C%20ISC%20Board%20Results%202024%3A%20Girls%20have%20outperformed%20boys%20in%20both%20ICSE%20(Class%2010)%20and%20ISC%20(Class%2012)%20with%20pass%20rates%20of%2099.65%25%20and%2098.92%25%2C%20respectively.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fafter-cbse-cisce-scraps-class-10-12-merit-lists-to-avoid-unhealthy-competition-5600074%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fafter-cbse-cisce-