20the%20road.%20The%20approaching%20sedan%20drove%20past%20the%20EcoSport%20driver's%20side%20from%20the%20opposite%20direction%20and%20narrowly%20missed%20hitting%20it%20by%20a%20few%20inches.%20The%20EcoSport%20driver%20did%20not%20retaliate%2C%20but%20the%20BMW%20took%20a%20U-turn%20and%20began%20tailing%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20driver%20realized%20that%20the%20car%20was%20being%20chased%2C%20and%20at%20a%20Y-junction%20on%20the%20deserted%20road%2C%20the%20BMW%20overtook%20and%20stopped%20in%20front%20of%20the%20EcoSport.%20Three%20men%20got%20out%20of%20the%20car%20and%20started%20walking%20toward%20the%20vehicle.%20The%20road%20rage%20victim%20chose%20to%20drive%20away%20to%20avoid%20any%20confrontation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-embed-height%3D%5C%22566%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FCarsIndia%2Fcomments%2F1ckpyem%2Fgoons_in_bmw_attacked_family_at_1_am_in_greater%2F%5C%22%3EGoons%20in%20BMW%20attacked%20family%20at%201%20AM%20in%20Greater%20Noida%2C%20this%20is%20so%20scary%20man%2C%20also%20shows%20the%20importance%20of%20dashcam%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cnby%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fuser%2FD_Invincible%2F%5C%22%3Eu%2FD_Invincible%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FCarsIndia%2F%5C%22%3ECarsIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chase%20continued%2C%20and%20the%20victim%20drove%20at%20high%20speeds.%20A%20frightened%20woman%20was%20heard%20calling%20someone%20for%20help%2C%20while%20another%20man%20was%20giving%20the%20driver%20directions%20toward%20their%20destination%2C%20the%20hospital.%20Four%20minutes%20later%2C%20the%20BMW%20overtook%20the%20vehicle%20again.%20The%20BMW's%20co-driver%20and%20two%20passengers%20in%20the%20rear%20seat%20got%20out%20of%20the%20vehicle%20and%20charged%20toward%20the%20EcoSport%2C%20throwing%20bottles%20at%20them.%20The%20victim%20reversed%20his%20car%20and%20took%20a%20sharp%20U-tur