20Montclair%2C%20New%20Jersey.%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20never%20had%20a%20real%20job.%20After%20graduating%20with%20a%20psychology%20degree%20in%202010%2C%20I%20went%20into%20business%20with%20my%20mom%2C%20Ann%20Lightfoot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20only%20other%20work%20experience%20was%20at%20an%20ice%20cream%20store%2C%20where%20I%20learned%20I%20wanted%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburned-out-entrepreneur-business-retreat-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eentrepreneurial%20life%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20don't%20like%20taking%20orders%20from%20someone%20else%20and%20seeing%20the%20freedom%20the%20store%20owner%20had%20made%20me%20want%20to%20create%20that%20for%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20I%20think%20it%20would've%20been%20helpful%20to%20learn%20how%20other%20companies%20operate%2C%20but%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20a%20good%20thing%20I'm%20not%20burdened%20by%20thinking%20about%20how%20something%20%26quot%3Bshould%26quot%3B%20be%20done.%20I%20can%20just%20do%20what%20works%20best%20for%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20first%20started%20a%20company%20that%20sold%20eyeglass%20necklaces%20and%20had%20some%20success%2C%20but%20we%20also%20started%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-professional-home-organizers-got-start-pandemic-business-grown-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehome%20organization%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202012%20as%20Done%20%26amp%3B%20Done%20Home.%20We%20realized%20we%20couldn't%20do%20both.%20Done%20%26amp%3B%20Done%20was%20bringing%20in%20more%20money%2C%20and%20we%20liked%20helping%20people%20more%20than%20selling%20a%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20started%20as%20a%20mother-daughter%20duo%20organizing%20closets%20and%20hauling%20trash%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20successful%20business%20with%2014%20employees.%20In%202023%2C%20we%20generated%20over%20%241.6%20million%20in%20revenue.%3C