0have%20three%20young%20boys%20and%2C%20like%20lots%20of%20parents%2C%20I%20struggle%20to%20balance%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworking-mom-two-jobs-burned-out-no-work-life-balance-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ework%20and%20family%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20because%20my%20mom%20and%20I%20live%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-buys-duplex-first-home-rental-income-helps-pay-mortgage-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo-family%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20bringing%20work%20home%20isn't%20a%20big%20deal.%20I%20often%20work%20on%20my%20laptop%20on%20the%20kitchen%20counter%20while%20my%20mom%20helps%20me%20with%20the%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiving%20in%20a%20two-family%20home%20has%20given%20us%20nothing%20but%20upsides.%20We%20rely%20on%20each%20other%20and%20have%20each%20other's%20backs%2C%20and%20one%20of%20us%20can%20run%20to%20the%20store%20if%20somebody%20needs%20milk.%20I%20absolutely%20love%20our%20setup%2C%20though%20I%20understand%20it's%20not%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mom%20and%20I%20have%20always%20been%20close%20and%20are%20very%20open%20with%20communicating%20our%20needs%20to%20each%20other%2C%20so%20that%20helps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20biggest%20piece%20of%20advice%20I%20have%20for%20anyone%20starting%20their%20own%20company%20is%20to%20know%20your%20math%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20noticed%20some%20small%20business%20owners%20are%20so%20busy%20handling%20day-to-day%20tasks%20that%20they%20don't%20take%20the%20time%20to%20understand%20the%20true%20financial%20workings%20of%20their%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20need%20to%20ask%20yourself%3A%20Where%20are%20you%20finding%20new%20clients%3F%20What%20does%20it%20cost%20to%20get%20them%3F%20What%20is%20your%20percentage%20of%20repeat%20business%3F%20What%20is%20your%20profit%20margin%3F%20Do%20you%20have%20savings%3F%20Is%20there%20anywhere%20you%20are%20misspending%3F%20Knowin