9-to-5%20salary.%20If%20Udo%20could%20do%20it%2C%20White%20thought%2C%20maybe%20he%20could%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThey%20saved%20and%20invested%20better%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhite%20started%20researching%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ffinancial-independence-retire-early%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFIRE%3C%2Fa%3E%20movement%20%E2%80%94%20Financial%20Independence%2C%20Retire%20Early%20%E2%80%94%20and%20pitched%20his%20plan%20to%20his%20wife%2C%20Lisa%2C%20who%20worked%20for%20a%20nonprofit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20had%20already%20been%20saving%20but%20decided%20to%20ramp%20up%20their%20savings%20and%20investments.%20White%20was%20making%20%24107%2C000%20a%20year%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20had%20a%20net%20worth%20of%20%24813%2C000%20but%20started%20following%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-much-do-i-need-to-retire%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E4%25%20rule%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20says%20you%20should%20only%20retire%20early%20if%20you%20can%20live%20off%204%25%20of%20your%20savings%20each%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20they%20could%20build%20a%20portfolio%20of%20%241%20million%2C%20they'd%20be%20able%20to%20use%20%2440%2C000%20a%20year%20on%20living%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20couple%20built%20a%20portfolio%20of%20over%20%241%20million%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhite%20said%20the%20main%20change%20he%20made%20was%20adjusting%20his%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20I%20had%20been%20socking%20away%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20into%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-reduce-taxes-when-withdrawing-from-401k-plan-retirement-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E401(k)%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20work%2C%20I%20had%20just%20picked%20random%20mutual%20funds%20that%20seemed%20good%20because%20they%20showed%20some%20good%20performance%20in%20prior%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnalyzing%20his%20plan%2C%20he%20discovered%20one%20fund%20he%20was%20investing%20in%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20high%20cost%26quot%3B%20and%20switched%20from%20mutual%20funds%20to%20lower-cost%20index%20funds.%20By%20tweaking%20the%20funds%20he%20included%20in%20his%20plan%2C%20he%20told%20BI%20he%20saved%20around%20%2465%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hardest%20part%20was%20waiting%2C%20White%20said.%20Once%20they'd%20cut%20their%20expenses%20and%20changed%20their%20investments%2C%20they%20had%20to%20wait%20for%20their%20savings%20to%20accumulate.%20They%20also%20started%20saving%2060%25%20of%20his%20pay%20and%20living%20off%20the%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThey%20retired%20and%20moved%20to%20Panama%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBy%202018%2C%20they%20had%20investments%2C%20assets%2C%20and%20savings%20worth%20over%20%241%20million%2C%20according%20to%20financial%20documents%20BI%20has%20viewed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20sold%20their%20house%20for%20%24267%2C800%20in%202018%20and%20rented%20a%20nearby%20apartment%20for%20a%20few%20months.%20White%20retired%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%20aged%2043%20%E2%80%94%20Lisa%20had%20already%20left%20her%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20their%20newfound%20freedom%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20relocate%20to%20Boquete%2C%20a%20small%20town%20in%20Panama%2C%20because%20of%20its%20warmer%20climate.%20%26quot%3BI've%20lived%20in%20Ohio%20pretty%20much%20my%20whole%20life%2C%20and%20I%20can't%20stand%20the%20winters%2C%26quot%3B%20White%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20moved%20to%20the%20mountains%20of%20Panama%2C%20and%20it%20was%2075%20degrees%20every%20day%20of%20the%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20sold%20their%20car%20and%20most%20of%20their%20belongings%20and%20packed%20the%20rest%20into%20a%20storage%20unit.%20The%20family%20moved%20with%20their%20daughter%2C%20then%20nine%2C%20in%20July%202019.%20They%20rented%20a%20three-bedroom%20house%20in%20a%20gated%20community%20for%20%241%2C100%20a%20month%20and%20didn't%20need%20a%20car.%20%26quot%3BWe'd%20walk%20every%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20started%20homeschooling%20their%20daughter%2C%20intending%20to%20place%20her%20in%20an%20international%20school%20later.%20But%2C%20they%20ended%20up%20homeschooling%20her%20for%20the%20three%20years%20they%20lived%20in%20Panama%2C%20because%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20lived%20off%20around%20%2450%2C000%20a%20year%2C%20slightly%20higher%20than%20anticipated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20couple%20moved%20back%20to%20the%20US%20to%20travel%20in%20an%20RV%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20moved%20back%20to%20the%20US%20in%20April%202022.%20Since%20October%2C%20the%20family%20has%20been%20traveling%20around%20Tennessee%2C%20Louisiana%2C%20Georgia%2C%20Indiana%2C%20Texas%2C%20and%20Arizona%20in%20an%20RV%2C%20which%20they%20bought%20but%20plan%20to%20sell%20after%20their%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20spending%20incredible%20amounts%20of%20time%20as%20a%20family%2C%20just%20like%20I%20wanted%2C%20ever%20since%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20been%20a%20dream%20come%20true.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20they're%20finished%20with%20their%20travels%2C%20they%20plan%20to%20move%20back%20to%20Ohio%20to%20give%20their%20daughter%2C%20who%20is%20now%2014%2C%20some%20stability.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20had%20our%20quality%20time%20together%2C%20and%20now%20she%20wants%20to%20spend%20more%20time%20with%20her%20friends%2C%26quot%3B%20White%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELisa%20wants%20to%20live%20near%20family%20again%20and%20plans%20to%20return%20to%20work%20part-time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20White%20is%20content%20to%20spend%20his%20time%20on%20hobbies%20like%20coding%2C%20learning%20Spanish%2C%20and%20writing%20his%20blog%2C%20%26quot%3BRoute%20to%20Retire.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20because%20we're%20not%20working%20right%20now%20doesn't%20mean%20we%20don't%20plan%20to%20ever%20work%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20White%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20that%20we%20have%20that%20choice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffire-early-retirement-couple-forties-panama-rv-rented-rv-homeschool-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714986001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6634cdca0dfb1341e902303c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffire-early-retirement-couple-forties-panama-rv-rented-rv-homeschool-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jim%20White%20shared%20how%20he%20reached%20FIRE%20%E2%80%94%20Financial%20Independence%2C%20Retire%20Early%20%E2%80%94%20and%20retired%20at%2043.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ehopkins%40insider.com%20(Ella%20Hopkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A44%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffire-early-retirement-couple-forties-panama-rv-rented-rv-homeschool-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Morgan%20Freeman%20to%20Be%20Honored%20at%20Monte-Carlo%20Television%20Festival%2C%20%E2%80%98The%20Gray%20House%E2%80%99%20to%20Premiere%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714986000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FMorgan-Freeman.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235992509%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Morgan%20Freeman%20will%20receive%20the%20Crystal%20Nymph%20Award%20at%20the%20Monte-Carlo%20Television%20Festival%2C%20which%20runs%20June%2014-18%20in%20Monaco.%20Freeman%20will%20receive%20the%20award%20at%20the%20opening%20ceremony%20from%20Prince%20Albert%20II%20of%20Monaco%2C%20in%20recognition%20of%20his%20television%20career.%20The%20festival%20will%20open%20with%20the%20world%20prem