%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662aabeb0dfb1341e9ff4907%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221999%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJake%20Ellowitz%20is%20the%20chief%20technology%20officer%20and%20cofounder%20of%20Termina.%3Cp%3ETermina%3B%20Nick%20Little%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20Seed%20100%20and%20Seed%2040%20lists%20are%20created%20based%20on%20data%20from%20Termina.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ETermina%20began%20with%20data%20on%20over%201%2C800%20investors%2C%20analyzing%2025%20success%20attributes%2C%20such%20as%20exits.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20analysis%20identifies%20skilled%20investors%20with%20a%20high%20likelihood%20of%20continued%20success.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fseed-100-best-early-stage-vc-investors-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESeed%20100%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fseed-40-best-women-early-stage-vc-investors-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESeed%2040%3C%2Fa%3E%20lists%20are%20derived%20from%20a%20statistical%20analysis%20of%20investor%20track%20records.%20We've%20been%20working%20with%20Business%20Insider%20to%20publish%20these%20lists%20for%20the%20past%20four%20years%2C%20but%20this%20is%20the%20first%20year%20we're%20doing%20so%20under%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftermina.ai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETermina%3C%2Fa%3E%20brand.%20Incubated%20by%20Tribe%20Capital%2C%20Termina%20is%20an%20AI-software%20platform%20that%20powers%20quantitative%20due%20diligence%20for%20leading%20investors%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20methodology%20is%20the%20same%20as%20it%20was%20in%20past%20years.%20It%20analyzes%20each%20investor's%20performance%20in%2025%20areas%20using%20Crunchbase%20and%20PitchBook%20data.%20Since%20one%20of%20our%20goals%20is%20to%20analyze%20investor's%20potential%20success%20rather%20than%20focus%20solely%20on%20past%20achievements%2C%20we%20only%20assess%20investors%20who%20have%20made%20a%20minimum%20of%20five%20investments%20between%202009%20and%202024.%20Our%20list%20includes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsolo-capitalists-startup-investors-shaking-up-venture-capital-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolo%20venture%20capitalists%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20angel%20investors%20who%20are%20assessed%20based%20on%20their%20investments%20in%20US%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20named%20to%20the%20list%2C%20seed%20investors%20must%20have%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EInvestments%20that%20performed%20well%2C%20including%20successful%20IPOs%20or%20acquisitions%20(exits%20that%20were%20meaningfully%20above%20%26quot%3Bliquidation%20preference%26quot%3B%20or%20showed%20increased%20company%20value%20rather%20than%20simply%20raising%20capital).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EShow%20intermediate%20signs%20of%20future%20success%20with%20seed%20investments%20that%20consistently%20receive%20follow-on%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EBe%20active%20in%20the%20seed-investing%20ecosystem%2C%20with%20moderate-to-high%20levels%20of%20activity%20over%20the%20past%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20each%20criterion%20is%20weighted%20equally%2C%20exits%20(IPOs%20or%20acquisitions)%20statistically%20have%20the%20most%20influence%20in%20differentiating%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%201%2C800%20investors%20met%20the%20above%20criteria%2C%20an%2018%25%20increase%20from%20last%20year.%20The%20seed-investor%20ecosystem%20grows%20every%20year%2C%20making%20the%20list%20more%20competitive.%20We're%20also%20delighted%20that%20there%20were%20187%20female%20candidates%20with%20sufficient%20data%2C%20a%20significant%20increase%20that%20allowed%20us%20to%20release%20an%20expanded%20Seed%2040%20list%20this%20year.%20Ten%20percent%20of%20all%20seed%20investors%20in%20scope%20were%20women%2C%20up%20from%208%25%20when%20the%20first%20Seed%20100%20was%20released%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20rankings%20had%2035%20new%20investors%2C%2021%20who%20improved%20their%20rank%2C%20and%2039%20with%20the%20same%20or%20lower%20rank%20as%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20is%20storming%20seed%20investing%20and%20beyond%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20reason%20we%20look%20at%20seed-stage%20investments%20is%20because%20they%20tend%20to%20be%20leading%20indicators%20of%20innovation%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%20OpenAI%20released%20their%20GPT-4%20model%20just%20over%20a%20year%20ago.%20The%20model%20reached%20an%20inflection%20point%20of%20capability%20that%20has%20ignited%20the%20imagination%20of%20entrepreneurs%20and%20investors%20worldwide.%20The%20result%20in%20just%20one%20year%20is%20the%20largest-ever%20rebalancing%20of%20how%20investors%20allocate%20seed%20capital%20across%20sectors.%20In%20our%20analysis%2C%20AI%20tech%20receives%20over%2016%25%20of%20all%20seed-investing%20capital%2C%20with%20a%20significant%20jump%20in%20the%2012%20months%20following%20GPT-4's%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20chart%20below%2C%20we%20show%20five%20seed-investment%20categories%20to%20contextualize%20the%20growth%20of%20AI%20investment.%20This%20is%20not%20an%20exhaustive%20view%20of%20seed-investment%20sectors.%20In%20this%20view%2C%20though%20there%20has%20been%20a%20steady%20expansion%20of%20AI%20investing%20at%20the%20seed%20stage%2C%20the%20jump%20last%20year%20clearly%20stands%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22For%20Seed%20100%20methodology%20post%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663291c6ec0c696569ffd587%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22637%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESource%3A%20Crunchbase%20and%20Termina%20analysis.%20The%20presented%20categories%20are%20not%20mutually%20exclusive%20or%20collectively%20exhaustive.%20Figures%20presented%20are%20the%20rolling%20annual%20fraction%20of%20total%20seed%20investment%20in%20the%20USA%20and%20Canada.%3Cp%3ETermina%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20believe%20AI%20will%20allow%20more%20seed-stage%20companies%20to%20bring%20products%20to%20market%20with%20less%20capital%2C%20similar%20to%20how%20cloud%20computing%20accelerated%20processes%20and%20reduced%20the%20capital%20required%20to%20launch%20products.%20If%20true%2C%20this%20will%20make%20seed-stage%20investing%20even%20more%20critical%20as%20AI%20begins%20to%20form%20the%20infrastructure%20that%20launches%20new%20tech%20products%20and%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJake%20Ellowitz%20is%20the%20chief%20technology%20officer%20and%20cofounder%20of%20Termina.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-termina-selected-ranked-seed-100-seed-40-lists-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714985102000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662abe4710dfcda4096395ec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-termina-selected-ranked-seed-100-seed-40-lists-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delve%20into%20Termina's%20methodology%20for%20assessing%20investors'%20performance%20for%20the%20data%20behind%20Business%20Insider's%20Seed%20100%20and%20Seed%2040%20lists.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jake%20Ellowitz%2C%20Termina)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-termina-selected-ranked-seed-100-seed-40-lists-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dashcam%20shows%20tornado%20obliterate%20Nebraska%20building%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714984943000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1