o%20massive%20fish%20deaths%20in%20southern%20Vietnam.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20climate%20crisis%20and%20human%20development%20threaten%20the%20Mekong%20Delta%2C%20a%20key%20global%20agricultural%20center.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDespite%20infrastructure%20measures%2C%20some%20farmers%20are%20still%20struggling%20to%20access%20water.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20weekslong%20drought%20across%20parts%20of%20southeast%20Asia%20has%20killed%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20fish%20in%20a%20reservoir%20in%20Vietnam%20and%20pushed%20a%20key%20metric%20for%20coffee%20prices%20to%20record%20levels%20%E2%80%94%20just%20two%20indicators%20of%20the%20kind%20of%20havoc%20the%20climate%20is%20wreaking%20on%20people%20and%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Vietnam%2C%20the%20maze%20of%20wetlands%20that%20comprise%20the%20Mekong%20Delta%20is%20called%20the%20country's%20%26quot%3Brice%20bowl%26quot%3B%20because%20of%20the%20vast%20agriculture%20it%20supports.%20The%20climate%20crisis%20and%20human%20development%20threaten%20the%20water%20the%20region%20relies%20on%2C%20especially%20in%20El%20Ni%C3%B1o%20years%20like%20this%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Vietnam's%20freshwater%20levels%20drop%2C%20salt%20water%20intrudes%2C%20causing%20massive%20economic%20devastation.%20From%202020%20to%202023%2C%20the%20Mekong%20Delta%20lost%2070%20trillion%20Vietnamese%20dong%2C%20or%20%242.96%20billion%2C%20annually%20because%20of%20salt%20intrusion%2C%20the%20country's%20Ministry%20of%20Natural%20Resources%20and%20the%20Environment%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fe.vnexpress.net%2Fnews%2Fenvironment%2Fmekong-delta-loses-3b-a-year-to-salt-intrusion-4723065.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20mid-March.%20Those%20figures%20are%20expected%20to%20climb%20in%20coming%20years%2C%20the%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Vietnam%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20heavily%20agricultural%20economy%2C%20the%20industry%20still%20accounted%20for%20about%2012%25%20of%20its%20GDP%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdata.worldbank.org%2Findicator%2FNV.AGR.TOTL.ZS%3Flocations%3DVN%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorld%20Bank%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20too%20early%20to%20know%20exactly%20how%20this%20year's%20drought%2C%20exacerbated%20by%20El%20Ni%C3%B1o%2C%20will%20affect%20harvests%20and%20exports.%20But%20early%20gauges%20indicate%20trouble%20for%20at%20least%20one%20key%20export.%20Vietnam's%20coffee%20association%20said%20in%20late%20March%20that%20exports%20of%20robusta%20coffee%20%E2%80%94%20the%20bean%20used%20in%20espresso%20and%20instant%20coffee%20%E2%80%94%20could%20decline%20as%20much%20as%2020%25%20in%20the%2012%20months%20ending%20in%20September%2C%20compared%20with%20the%20same%20period%20last%20year.%20Vietnam%20is%20the%20world's%20largest%20robusta%20producer%2C%20and%20futures%20prices%20for%20the%20bean%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoffee-prices-vietnam-robusta-futures-high-asia-expensive-drought-espresso-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehit%20a%2016-year%20high%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20southern%20Vietnam%2C%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20fish%20died%20in%20a%20reservoir%20last%20month%20as%20temperatures%20peaked%20over%20100%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20and%20no%20rain%20fell%20for%20weeks%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.france24.com%2Fen%2Flive-news%2F20240501-mass-fish-die-off-in-vietnam-as-heatwave-roasts-southeast-asia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAFP%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Residents%20blamed%20the%20weather%20and%20the%20reservoir's%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20could%20not%20locate%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20reservoir%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vietnamese%20fisherman%20collects%20dead%20fish%20in%20a%20reservoir.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi