ons%20from%20the%20Mac%2C%20iPad%2C%20and%20wearables.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECook's%20limited%20remarks%20on%20China's%20iPhone%20sales%20raised%20questions%20on%20Friday's%20call%20from%20analysts%20who%20compared%20Apple's%20data%20with%20independent%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20simple%20question%20is%2C%20when%20we%20look%20at%20the%20data%20points%20that%20have%20been%20repeatedly%20reported%20throughout%20the%20course%20of%20this%20quarter%2C%20I'm%20curious%2C%20Tim%2C%20you%20know%2C%20what%20are%20we%20missing%3F%26quot%3B%20asked%20Wells%20Fargo%20analyst%20Aaron%20Rakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECook%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20third-party%20data%20points%20on%20the%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20at%20the%20research%20firms%20said%20the%20difference%20comes%20from%20how%20analysts%20and%20Apple%20calculate%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20quarter%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20tracked%20a%20year-on-year%20decline%20in%20total%20value%20generated%20by%20iPhones%20in%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20IDC%20analyst%20Will%20Wong%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-05-03%2Fapple-s-surprise-iphone-china-growth-leaves-lingering-questions%3Futm_source%3Dgoogle%26utm_medium%3Dbd%26cmpId%3Dgoogle%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%20%3C%2Fa%3Eafter%20Apple's%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20selling%20price%20plays%20a%20key%20role%20in%20explaining%20the%20difference.%20IDC%20counted%20the%20prices%20customers%20paid%2C%20while%20Apple%20likely%20uses%20another%20price%20level%2C%20such%20as%20factory%20price%2C%20in%20its%20financial%20reporting%2C%20Wong%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20discrepancy%20may%20also%20come%20from%20newer%20and%20more%20expensive%20models%20making%20up%20a%20bigger%20portion%20of%20purchases%2C%20which%20could%20drive%20up%20revenue%2C%20even%20if%20total%20unit%20sales%20declined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECook%2C%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.