20in.%20It%20equips%20families%20with%20practical%20ways%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20distress%20created%20by%20the%20disease.%20It%E2%80%99s%20about%20keeping%20the%20children%20engaged%20with%20educational%20sessions%20so%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20miss%20out%20on%20school%2C%20and%20teaching%20the%20parents%20new%20skills%20that%20could%20be%20a%20source%20of%20livelihood%20when%20they%20return%20to%20their%20respective%20hometowns%20after%20their%20child%E2%80%99s%20long%20treatment%2C%20the%20duo%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20to%20one%20example%2C%20Ankeet%20recalls%20the%20example%20of%20a%20parent%20who%20used%20to%20run%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F259515%2Findian-food-recipes-pakora-map-of-india-cuisine-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Epuri%20bhajiya%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E(a%20fast%20food%20stall)%20stall%20in%20Siliguri%2C%20West%20Bengal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20he%20came%20to%20live%20at%20our%20centre%20for%20his%20child%E2%80%99s%20treatment%20(which%20lasted%20six%20months)%2C%20he%20had%20to%20sell%20his%20cart%20back%20home.%20He%20was%20worried%20about%20what%20would%20happen%20to%20his%20livelihood.%20But%20during%20his%20time%20here%2C%20he%20learnt%20how%20to%20make%20%3Cem%3Evada%20pav%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20started%20selling!%20The%20business%20was%20a%20huge%20success%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGirish%20pitches%20in%20with%20another%20heartwarming%20story.%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20parents%20was%20a%20soldier%20who%20quit%20and%20came%20to%20our%20Mumbai%20centre%20when%20his%20child%20was%20admitted.%20But%20in%20the%20weeks%20that%20followed%2C%20he%20saw%20how%20well%20his%20son%20was%20being%20cared%20for%20at%20the%20centre.%20That%20enabled%20him%20to%20go%20back%20to%20his%20duty%20peacefully.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20duo%20encourages%20both%20parent