%20the%20structures%20with%20open%20spaces%2C%20inward-looking%20homes%20with%20courtyards%20and%20huge%20windows%20helped%20to%20keep%20the%20home%20naturally%20cool.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamira%20Rathod%2C%20an%20architect%20and%20designer%2C%20applied%20similar%20techniques%20to%20make%20a%20%E2%80%9CCool%20House%E2%80%9D%20located%20in%20Gujarat.%20The%20architect%20decided%20to%20utilise%20the%20wind%2C%20design%20and%20cooling%20materials%20to%20build%20and%20cool%20down%20the%20house.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20architect%20suggests%20using%20the%20wind%20in%20a%20way%20that%20it%20travels%20through%20the%20home%20making%20it%20cooler.%20For%20the%20cool%20house%20located%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20she%20used%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctrack-like%20design%20with%20rooms%20on%20either%20side%20of%20the%20house%20with%20a%20courtyard%20to%20help%20the%20wind%20circulate.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201067px)%20100vw%2C%201067px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F71e1f2ce8e654135b509da9fba6c6619_311592766_142412935197808_3738696823372802622_n-1680175563.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221067%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Going%20back%20to%20traditional%20designs%20and%20making%20use%20of%20natural%20materials%20to%20build%20a%20naturally%20cool%20house.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F71e1f2ce8e654135b509da9fba6c6619_311592766_142412935197808_3738696823372802622_n-1680175563.jpg%201067w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F71e1f2ce8e654135b509da9fba6c6619_311592766_142412935197808_3738696823372802622_n-1680175563-240x300.jpg%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F71e1f2ce8e654135b509da9fba6c6619_311592766_142412935197808_3738696823372802622_n-1680175563-500x625.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.