%20grow%20fruits%20in%20her%20rooftop%20garden%2C%20which%20can%20help%20you%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FJayanti-Sahoo-1713363481.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jayanti%20grows%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20including%20chikoo%2C%20tomatoes%2C%20and%20brinjals%20on%20her%20350%20sq%20ft%20terrace.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FJayanti-Sahoo-1713363481.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FJayanti-Sahoo-1713363481-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FJayanti-Sahoo-1713363481-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FJayanti-Sahoo-1713363481-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FJayanti-Sahoo-1713363481-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347570%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EJayanti%20grows%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20including%20chikoo%2C%20tomatoes%2C%20and%20brinjals%20on%20her%20350%20sq%20ft%20terrace.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGrow%20your%20own%20fruits%20with%20these%208%20tips%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Place%20the%20fruit%20trees%20strategically%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Jayanti%2C%20urban%20gardeners%20should%20first%20ensure%20a%20proper%20drainage%20system%20on%20the%20terrace%20so%20that%20it%20does%20not%20absorb%20excess%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSecondly%2C%20keep%20your%20pots%20such%20that%20they%20are%20placed%20above%20the%20beams%20and%20walls%20of%20the%20rooms%20that%20are%20belo