and%20then%20those%20which%20are%20predominantly%20said%20to%20be%20French%20style%20because%20of%20the%20arches%20and%20pillars%20and%20certain%20other%20details.%20Gratitude%20Heritage%20falls%20in%20the%20third%20category.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332749%2Fex-banker-sunando-sen-built-tanhau-sustainable-himalayan-homestay-corbett-restore-wildlife%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20restoration%20process%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20care%20was%20taken%20to%20not%20upset%20anything%20of%20the%20old%20home.%20%E2%80%9CNo%20walls%20were%20broken%20and%20no%20trees%20were%20cut%2C%E2%80%9D%20Siddarth%20shares.%20He%20goes%20on%20to%20narrate%20an%20anecdote%20of%20how%20a%20mango%20tree%20in%20the%20courtyard%20was%20hindering%20the%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20chopping%20it%20off%2C%20they%20called%20in%20%E2%80%98tree%20doctors%E2%80%99%20who%20pulled%20the%20tree%20out%20of%20the%20way%20until%20work%20was%20complete.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Ftravel-6_11zon-1713764375.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jyoti%20and%20her%20son%20Siddarth%2C%20the%20duo%20behind%20the%20restoration%20and%20managing%20of%20the%20Gratitude%20Heritage%20homestay%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Ftravel-6_11zon-1713764375.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Ftravel-6_11zon-1713764375-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Ftravel-6_11zon-1713764375-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Ftravel-6_11zon-1713764375-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%